OL,4,CGoogle may cut pay of staff who work
OL,5,Cfrom home
OL,6, Google employees in the US who opt to
OL,7, work from home permanently may get a
OL,8, pay cut.
OL,10,FThe technology giant has developed a
OL,11,Fpay calculator that lets employees see
OL,12,Fthe effects of working remotely or
OL,13,Fmoving offices.
OL,15,FSome remote employees, especially those
OL,16,Fwith a long commute, could have their
OL,17,Fpay cut without changing address.
OL,19,FGoogle has no plans at this time to
OL,20,Fimplement the policy in the UK.
